arts.ttl: English coach Liam Rosenior's first season in charge of Strasbourg is still going well
arts.sum: Liam Rosenior’s first season in charge of Strasbourg is going well and the Alsace-based club moved provisionally up to sixth place in Ligue 1 after winning 1-0 at Nantes on Sunday. Third-placed Nice hosted Lyon later Sunday needing a win to move level on points with second-placed Marseille.
